sources.description:
Street Racer - After serving time for a tragic accident, in which a young boy is crippled, an illegal street racer finds himself dragged back into the world of high speed competition on the side streets and highways of Los Angeles.
2008.  Stars: Clint Browning, Dorothy Drury, Robert Pike Daniel
